text: Ayane ratrini pagatiloki pravesimpa jestunnadu mariyu pagatini ratriloki pravesimpa jestunnadu mariyu suryacandrulanu niyamabad'dhuluga cesi unnadu. Avi tama tama paridhilo, nirnita vyavadhilo tirugutu unnayi. Ayane allah! Mi prabhuvu, visvasamrajyadhikaram ayanade! Mariyu ayananu vadali miru vedukune varu, kharjura bijampai nunna poraku kuda yajamanulu karu
